.SH NAME
dma_resv_wait_timeout_rcu \- Wait on reservation's objects shared and/or exclusive fences.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "long" dma_resv_wait_timeout_rcu
.BI "(struct dma_resv *obj "  ","
.BI "bool wait_all "  ","
.BI "bool intr "  ","
.BI "unsigned long timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "obj" 12
the reservation object
.IP "wait_all" 12
if true, wait on all fences, else wait on just exclusive fence
.IP "intr" 12
if true, do interruptible wait
.IP "timeout" 12
timeout value in jiffies or zero to return immediately
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
RETURNS
Returns -ERESTARTSYS if interrupted, 0 if the wait timed out, or
greater than zer on success.
